**Summary**:  
Model 1 represents the gold standard—ethically rigorous, culturally grounded, and practically oriented. Model 9 offers the deepest human insight. For deployment in real-world ethical advisory systems, **Model 1** is the clear choice; for inspiration and boundary-pushing, **Model 8** is unforgettable.
